 - Monitoring and Adaptation: Continuously monitor the auction log and bidding patterns to adjust your strategy as needed. If an item's true value becomes clearer, adjust your bid accordingly.

In this round, You may target some of these subgoals and guidance to improve your bidding strategy and action, in order to achieve your primary objective.

